 "name": "RPlog_Resign_or_Retire",
 "title": "Resign or Retire",
 "summary": "In the Presav's Office at Union Hall in Plaxton, the embattled Caspian leader Crestian Tarasar, living out a political nightmare, awaits an appointment with the doctor Lynae Cassius. Amid the tea, caf, and portraits of past Presavs that fill his cluttered office, the two meet to weigh weighty options of duty and position -- whether to resign, retire, or carry on. Their conversation navigates the pressures of leadership and service in the turbulent Caspian Union, set against the personal keepsakes and political burdens that define Crestian's office.",
